Package cs2030.simulator

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030.simulator.Result
  • public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable class for storing results.

    Since it is immutable, and we only print out its results as a whole, all its fields are private final: (1) a double time: time of the event (2) a Customer object customer: customer involved in the event (null if there isn't one) (3) a eventType: type of the event (4) a Server object server: server involved in the event (5) a boolean isCustomerEvent: indicating the rough type of the event, so that output can be different.
